 It might come as a surprise to academics in South Africa but the purchasin=
g power of their salaries, on average, is now higher than that of their cou=
nterparts in Canada, the UK and New Zealand, according to a survey of 46 Co=
mmonwealth universities. However South African academics earn 6% less than =
those in Australia =96 the top-ranked country when cost of living is taken =
into account.<br><a href=3D"http://www.universityworldnews.com/article.php?=
